snippet.title: Koboo: The Tree Spirit - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Koboo: The Tree Spirit on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/718190/Koboo_The_Tree_Spirit/

Koboo: The Tree Spirit is an rogue-lite action adventure where you befriend animals and defend the forest from hunters and an expanding industry.
